            <title>[CXF-2788] Bus.shutdown() did not close all the created Jms connection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-2788</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The jmsListener in JmsDestination uses SingleConnectionFactory to create connection.   SingleConnectionFactory is a proxy class , it actually does not close the target connection . We need to call SingleConnectionFactory.distroy() to close the connection when bus shutdown . &lt;/p&gt;</description>
